Example

Sketch the graphs of the following periodic functions showing all relevant values:

  1. \(\begin{align} f(t) = \begin{cases} t^2/2 &0 < t < 4 \\ 8 & 4 < t < 6 \qquad f(t+8)=f(t) \\ 0 & 6 < t < 8 \end{cases} \end{align} \)
  2. \( f(t) = 2t - t^2 \qquad 0 < t < 2 \qquad f(t+2) = f(t) \)
